&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;7-database-comparison&#34;&gt;7. Database Comparison
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Function:&lt;/strong&gt; Provide a standard database for medical staff to compare data.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/Group_website/Group_website/p/module-wise-requirement-analysis-documentation/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%878.png&#34;
